{"tid":2337443,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（垃圾藍媒）星島集團明年1月1日推無薪假、每月4天　為期3個月","createTime":"2020-12-23T09:45:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-23T14:05:12.000Z","uid":204475,"like":17,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"8b1797389faeb4880bff0bf4c1572f0bbf8b03eb","tid":2337443,"uid":204475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T09:45:32.000Z","msg":"據星島集團 （01105） 內部公告，指疫情愈趨嚴峻，對媒體行業打擊極大，為保集團長遠穩健，員工明年1月1日起，需要放取無薪假期，為期3個月，每位星島員工每月須放取4天無薪假期。<br />\n<br />\n公告指，管理層希望得到同事們的理解，人事部會函致各受影響同事，一切將按勞工條例處理。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"268f299d1d6c5e4b790e073c07fe01d2c4bc6a4e","tid":2337443,"uid":284432,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T09:56:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c8788a79bf9e6fa9178571ed7ffb4c20e5697002","tid":2337443,"uid":51271,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T09:57:31.000Z","msg":"抵啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfd5819df31dac1f0076c4abbec7002f69a33dfb","tid":2337443,"uid":59976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T09:58:13.000Z","msg":"仲打藍媒工班人根本就抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fa8974545238775728acb3896a316b94bd350cf","tid":2337443,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T10:08:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/potion.gif\" class=\"hkg